      "comment": "NITRO'S IZZY (1) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 10 lengths seventh (17.94) last time in a Novice race at this track over 300m. Well worth another try. ZATARA STORM (8) doesn't win out of turn. Finished second (17.28) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Will give a great sight again. MILKY BAR KID (2) comes off an average effort last start when fifth at this track over 300m behind Radio Ramsgate (17.84) in a Novice race. The form out of last race has been strong. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. ORANA REX (6) did a good job to finish second last time out over 300m at this track (17.52) in a Novice race, the second top-three finish on the trot.",
